					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That sounds like typical LCD to me, all of them have viewing angle dependent color and brightness. Image gets darker when viewed below and brighter when above, and at more extreme angles some color will go negative even.<br />Some panel technologies have much less pronounced effect, but those tend to be much more expensive too.</div>

					
